com.fortyoneconcepts.valjogen.model

Class Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fortyoneconcepts.valjogen.model.ModelBase
      • com.fortyoneconcepts.valjogen.model.Type
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Model
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArrayType, ObjectType, PrimitiveType

    public abstract class Type
extends ModelBase
    Information about a type that a model use or refer to. Actual types are divided into 3 concrete subclasses depending on the category of the type. I.e. if the type is a primitive, an array or an object.
